{"tid":1211276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈15米內直射 警棍毆已被制服示威者 警濫用武力涉違國際法","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:39:04.000Z","uid":1575,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"497df4166e4238cb68372b5b31494791f2cbe074","tid":1211276,"uid":1575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59708793?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=video_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3TU7-xX-Mk77sp0MSeaoqu7B0EhPt5R1BgpX-JNY1GbYryTxmyIs_9Y6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708793%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dvideo_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3TU7-xX-Mk77sp0MSeaoqu7B0EhPt5R1BgpX-JNY1GbYryTxmyIs_9Y6k&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvyWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=c3e8c6a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708793%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dvideo_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3TU7-xX-Mk77sp0MSeaoqu7B0EhPt5R1BgpX-JNY1GbYryTxmyIs_9Y6k&h=c95bb97e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59708793?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=video_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3TU7-xX-Mk77sp0MSeaoqu7B0EhPt5R1BgpX-JNY1GbYryTxmyIs_9Y6k</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民權觀察批評有至少兩宗警察以警棍持續毆打已被制服的示威者的事件，有示威者即使已背向警方離開，但「速龍小隊」的警員仍以警棍襲擊示威者的背部，武力的使用是明顯過量，超出驅散或拘捕示威者的目的。涉事的警員的行為更可能涉及刑事成份，包括嚴重傷害他人身體的罪行。</span><br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織香港分會總幹事譚萬基指，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方向行動相當和平的示威者使用催淚彈及胡椒彈有違國際法</span>，警方以少數暴力行為作前題，以圖合理化向大部份和平示威者使用過度武力。他指催淚氣體及橡膠子彈等武器可致重傷，嚴重可致死，而這些發射物武器難以對準目標，攻擊任意，容易濫傷無辜，不應用作驅散和平示威者之用，而過份動武反令現場情況更加緊張，令衝突加劇，呼籲警方不要一再向和平示威者濫用警力，<span style=\"color: red;\">同時提醒警方向已被制服的個人或示威者動武同樣不合法。</span>"},{"pid":"041bc0c506cd741fe97d38a03a3e4a3c1d669a53","tid":1211276,"uid":5822,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"提你老母咩 一係就做野啦仆街"},{"pid":"01ae0a7e46073b67beccd5b7dfb481816ed6a973","tid":1211276,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eade1acda23b06137a3650d9b7678e4e46e253aa","tid":1211276,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"香港有法律既咩? 國際法有用既咩?"}]}